window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>A troubled young couple on a cross-country road trip takes a wrong turn in the Nevada desert.</p> <p>A voodoo spirit makes a bloody pact with a house cat.</p> <p>A father’s confrontation with his young son’s bully turns violent.</p> <p>An elderly man gets personalized messages in a fortune cookie.</p> <p>A home invasion takes an unexpected turn.</p> <p>A medieval monastery is infested with an ancient, predatory evil.</p> <p>A used-car salesman makes a purchase from a time-traveling madman.</p> <p>These are nine odd tales. No more, no less.</p> <p>Stories included:</p> <p></p> <ul> <li>\"Killer on the Road\"</li> <li>\"Traffic\"</li> <li>\"A Song of Sixpence\"</li> <li>\"The Merry-Go-Round Broke Down\"</li> <li>\"Daetana Dash\"</li> <li>\"Bully\"</li> <li>\"Precious Blood\"</li> <li>\"A Moment of Clarity\"</li> <li>\"Fred and Ol' Mama\"</li> </ul>"; 
